  "descriptionText": "Beneteau Oceanis 51.1 for sale 2019This Beneteau Oceanis 51.1 for sale 2019 is in good condition, and ready to be used.The vat has been paid in Europe. She has had only one owner, a private owner, who made sure this Beneteau Oceanis 51.1 for sale 2019 received regularly service. The following service was made in September 2021 : anodes, priming, antifouling, as well as prop-speed on propeller and shaft. She is berthed in Valencia, Spain and available for immediate viewings and delivery.With taut lines, a stepped hull and a stylish deck plan, this sailing yacht model, the Beneteau Oceanis 51.1 for sale 2019, was the first of a new generation. Easy to handle, comfortable and smart, the number of customizations available had been increased to provide more than 700 combinations. One third of the Beneteau Oceanis 51.1 for sale 2019's hull is now stepped. In addition to the aesthetics of this flared shape, the new hull shape creates additional interior space allowing for exciting new layouts on a boat this size. With emphasis on taut cruiser lines, the Beneteau Oceanis 51.1 for sale 2019 is a joy to move around and reassuringly safe. Her spacious cockpit, many relaxation and sun bathing areas, as well as an aft swim platform, promise true comfort. Her large hull portholes bathe the boat in light and elegantly emphasize the interior design by Nauta Design creating a unique atmosphere through woodwork ambiances and sleek design features.",
  "descriptionHtml": "<p><strong>Beneteau Oceanis&nbsp;51.1 for&nbsp;sale&nbsp;2019</strong></p><p>This<strong>&nbsp;Beneteau Oceanis 51.1 for&nbsp;</strong><strong>sale&nbsp;2019</strong>&nbsp;is in good condition, and ready to be used.</p><p>The vat has been paid in Europe. She has had only one owner, a private owner, who made sure this&nbsp;<strong>Beneteau Oceanis 51.1 for&nbsp;</strong><strong>sale&nbsp;2019</strong>&nbsp;received regularly service. The following service was made in September 2021 : anodes, priming, antifouling, as well as prop-speed on propeller and shaft. She is berthed in Valencia, Spain and available for immediate viewings and delivery.</p><p>With taut lines, a stepped hull and a stylish deck plan, this sailing yacht model, the&nbsp;<strong>Beneteau Oceanis&nbsp;51.1 for&nbsp;</strong><strong>sale&nbsp;2019</strong>, was the first of a new generation. Easy to handle, comfortable and smart, the number of customizations available had been increased to provide more than 700 combinations. One third of the&nbsp;<strong>Beneteau Oceanis&nbsp;51.1 for&nbsp;</strong><strong>sale&nbsp;2019'</strong>s hull is now stepped. In addition to the aesthetics of this flared shape, the new hull shape creates additional interior space allowing for exciting new layouts on a boat this size. With emphasis on taut cruiser lines, the&nbsp;<strong>Beneteau Oceanis&nbsp;51.1 for&nbsp;</strong><strong>sale&nbsp;2019</strong>&nbsp;is a joy to move around and reassuringly safe. Her spacious cockpit, many relaxation and sun bathing areas, as well as an aft swim platform, promise true comfort. Her large hull portholes bathe the boat in light and elegantly emphasize the interior design by Nauta Design creating a unique atmosphere through woodwork ambiances and sleek design features.</p>",
